T%E1%BA%A1p-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-4TfB7KhYyldLQLeNIG5GAQ">Tạp vịnh kỳ 1 - 雜詠其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-63sQ6igz79c8AB4tN4pK2g">Quách Dực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/V%C4%83n-thi-%C3%B4ng-C%C3%A1t-Xuy%C3%AAn-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-thu-c%E1%BB%ADu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%ADu-d%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%A1ch-trung-ngo%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BB%87nh-k%C3%BD-th%E1%BB%8B-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-zxe4JuRL35dNFOqMX3q4Rw">Văn thi ông Cát Xuyên tiên sinh thu cửu nguyệt nhị thập cửu dạ khách trung ngoạ bệnh ký thị kỳ 2 - 聞詩翁葛川先生秋九月二十九夜客中臥病寄示其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
